description:
A Gate Keeper from Germany.
Although Japanese, she resides in Germany because her father works there. She is also assigned by New York Headquarters to eliminate Invader executives in Japan. Like Megumi, she also talks to herself and is also an anti social.
In battlefield, she serves as the navigator of Jim and Jun. With her Gate of Sensors, she perceives abilities and or location that will happen in 10 seconds (max).
name: Sakimori Misao
